title: United Kingdom 7 Year Note Yield
description: UK 7 Year Bond Yield was 3.56 percent on Thursday November 3, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 7 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 5.73 in July of 2007. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 7Y.
author: Department of Treasury, UK
